法医报告称，泰勒·斯威夫特巴西演唱会粉丝因中暑死亡https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-death-at-taylor-swift-brazil-gig-caused-by-heat-exhaustion-says-forensics-report-3563440?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=取证报告称泰勒·斯威夫特在巴西演出时因热力衰竭而死亡Emma WilkesWed, 27 Dec 2023 18:00:10 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3563440 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-2-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰勒斯威夫特" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-2-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-2-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-2-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-2-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-2-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-2-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>安娜·克拉拉·贝尼维德斯 (Ana Clara Benevides) 在演出期间晕倒后死亡，演出时的气温接近 40 度</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-death-at-taylor-swift-brazil-gig-caused-by-heat-exhaustion-says-forensics-report-3563440">法医报告称，范在泰勒·斯威夫特巴西演唱会上因中暑死亡的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-2-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰勒斯威夫特" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-2-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-2-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-2-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-2-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-2-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-2-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一份法医报告得出结论，上个月在巴西举行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>演唱会中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-says-shes-devastated-by-death-of-fan-before-concert-show-in-brazil-3542686">一名歌迷因中暑死亡</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/taylor-swift-the-eras-tour-concert-movie-3513715">“泰勒·斯威夫特：时代之旅”音乐会电影评论：这就是电影院（泰勒的版本）</a></strong></li></ul><p> 11 月 17 日，23 岁的安娜·克拉拉·贝尼维德斯 (Ana Clara Benevides) 在 38 度高温下的演出中晕倒。几小时后，她因心脏骤停在当地一家医院去世。</p><p>在她去世的消息传出后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-says-shes-devastated-by-death-of-fan-before-concert-show-in-brazil-3542686">斯威夫特在社交媒体上表示，她对这一消息感到“震惊”</a> ，后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-postpones-rio-de-janeiro-show-due-to-extreme-heat-3542843">由于极端气温，取消了在该市举行的接下来的演出</a>。据广泛报道，球迷不被允许将水带入尼尔顿桑托斯体育场。</p><p>美联社（通过<a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/taylor-swift-fan-death-rio-forensics-report-b2470057.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《独立</em></a>报》）看到的里约热内卢法医研究所的报告称，贝尼维德斯因受热导致心肺骤停。它还说她没有任何可能导致她死亡的既存疾病或药物滥用。</p><p>分析她尸体的法医专家在文件中表示，由于高温，她“肺部严重受损并突然死亡”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3563443" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3563443" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3563443" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-3-1.jpg" alt="泰勒斯威夫特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-3-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-3-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-3-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-3-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-3-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/taylor-swift-james-devaney-3-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3563443" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒·斯威夫特：图片来源：James Devaney/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>组织者 T4F 没有立即回应<a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/ap">美联社</a>的置评请求。贝尼维德斯去世几天后，首席执行官塞拉菲姆·阿布鲁 (Serafim Abreu)​​ 在一段视频中表示，该公司将改变在极端高温下举办活动的协议，并承诺将为她的家人提供帮助。在她去世后，斯威夫特还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-meets-with-family-of-ana-clara-benevides-before-sao-paulo-show-3549581">与她的家人会面</a>。</p><p>与此同时，里约热内卢警方已对这起悲剧展开刑事调查，周三在一份声明中表示，在分析法医报告后，“组织该活动的公司代表将被传唤出庭作证。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/father-of-fan-who-died-before-taylor-swift-concert-pays-tribute-to-daughter-3543502">贝尼维德斯去世后，他的父亲接受<em>《圣保罗页</em>报》采访，</a>称赞他的女儿“快乐又聪明”。</p><p> “我失去了我唯一的女儿，一个快乐又聪明的女孩。她明年四月即将从心理学专业毕业，攒钱，”他说。 “我无法用语言来表达我的痛苦。她为了实现梦想而离家出走，回来时却死了。”</p><p>在其他消息中，斯威夫特与猫王<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elvis-presley">埃尔维斯·普雷斯利 (Elvis Presley)</a>并列成为 Billboard 200 排行榜<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-ties-with-elvis-presleys-solo-artist-record-for-most-weeks-atop-billboard-200-3563402">上单人歌手最多周排名第一的纪录</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-death-at-taylor-swift-brazil-gig-caused-by-heat-exhaustion-says-forensics-report-3563440">法医报告称，范在泰勒·斯威夫特巴西演唱会上因中暑死亡的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
